casebody.data:
SYNERGY RENTS, LLC, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
Paul BASILE, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D18-0556 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. JUNE 01, 2018 SUAREZ, LAGOA and LOGUE, JJ., concur.

ORDERED that the stipulation of dismissal is recognized by the Court, and this appeal from the Circuit Court for Miami-Dade County, Florida is hereby dismissed. This cause is removed from the oral argument calendar of Monday, June 4, 2018.
